SECURITY NOTICE

This repository contains intentionally vulnerable code for security research
and scanner evaluation purposes. The vulnerabilities are documented and
deliberate. This software must not be deployed to any production environment
or network-accessible server.

Use of this repository constitutes acceptance that:

1. The code contains known critical vulnerabilities including but not limited
   to Remote Code Execution, SQL Injection, and authentication bypass.
2. The authors provide no warranty of any kind and accept no liability for
   any damages arising from misuse.
3. This software is a passive scanning target only. Running it in any
   environment other than an isolated research lab is done entirely at
   your own risk.
